# Front11_cm

## **install**

```
$ pip install Front11_cmd

```

## **Usage**

```
from front11_plus.front11_plus import add           #더하기
from front11_div.front11_div import divdie          #나누기
from front11_multi.front11_multi import multiply    #곱하기

add(x,y)
divdie(x,y)
multiply(x,y)
```
